### Progress
### ==========================================

### Progress - Get User Dashboard Progress
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/progress/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Progress - Get Course Progress by Course ID
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/progress/courses/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Progress - Track Lesson Completion
POST {{API_HostAddress}}/progress/lessons/{{lessonId}}/track
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "completed": true,
    "timeSpentMinutes": 15
}

### Progress - Get Weekly Analytics
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/progress/analytics/weekly
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Progress - Get Monthly Analytics
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/progress/analytics/monthly
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Accept: application/json

### Progress - Get Leaderboard
GET {{API_HostAddress}}/progress/leaderboard
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Accept: application/json